{"tid":1891266,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［兒時回憶］新天地教令我聯想到天地會總舵主陳近南","createTime":"2020-02-21T17:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T17:02:42.000Z","uid":349653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d977cd4b29a1e9375fdb4bd86e42f02ea8a7f472","tid":1891266,"uid":349653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"依個教同基督教應該冇關係嘅<br />\n<br />\n新天地異端教會全名稱為&ldquo;新天地耶穌教證據帳幕聖殿&rdquo;（簡稱：新天地耶穌教會），韓國基督教界一般稱之為&ldquo;新天地&rdquo;。&ldquo;新天地耶穌教證據帳幕聖殿&rdquo;教會名稱中的&ldquo;新天地&rdquo;取自於啟示錄21中的新天新地，&ldquo;證據帳幕聖殿&rdquo;取自於15章5節內容（此處韓文聖經中有&ldquo;證據帳幕的聖殿&rdquo;字句，而中文和合本聖經中對應的詞句為&ldquo;存法櫃的殿&rdquo;）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ocbf.ca/2012/religion/religions/budda/5488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Focbf.ca%2F2012%2Freligion%2Freligions%2Fbudda%2F5488&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAFuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=fb8f4281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ocbf.ca/2012/religion/religions/budda/5488</a>"}]}